Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.16,0:22:01.28,Yellow,,0,0,0,,I al pròxim Conan: "El cas de la placa perduda"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.88,0:22:07.20,Songs,,0,0,0,,Asa ga kuru tabi kimi no koto omou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.40,0:22:13.12,Songs,,0,0,0,,ta soba ni ireba shiawase datta!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.44,0:22:19.80,Songs,,0,0,0,,Toki na tatsu koto ni tobiete naiteta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.00,0:22:24.60,Songs,,0,0,0,,kawari yuku hito no kokoro ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.28,0:22:32.72,Songs,,0,0,0,,Nozomanakereba...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.76,0:22:38.56,Songs,,0,0,0,,ushiwanai no niiii...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.16,0:22:45.40,Songs,,0,0,0,,motomezuni ha iranai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.60,0:22:52.60,Songs,,0,0,0,,donna mirai ha kono saki ni atte moooo...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.24,0:22:59.64,Songs,,0,0,0,,Yume wo mita ato de kimi ha mada tookute!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.84,0:23:05.20,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kimochi dake saki hashite karamawari.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.40,0:23:12.72,Songs,,0,0,0,,Hana no ame ha furu kono michi ha kawarazu!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.12,0:23:19.96,Songs,,0,0,0,,Ude wo karame arukitai naaaa!
